text: <!channel>: Friday is Spencer's birthday! :tada: make sure to get in your birthday wishes before then, or you'll miss him. (Happy Birthday, Spencer!)
If you want to start partying before the party tonight, have a honey whiskey cupcake from the walnut table and top it with some whiskey glaze. Or have a shot of the glaze, I don't judge.
Thanks <@U0261PCRQ>  alongside that tasty awesomeness is a holiday box of goodies from our friends at Aarra. Help yourself!
